- Aggregation phase: **~30-40% reduction** (58.82 → ~35-41 ms) due to 2-5x CompactHashTable speedup
- Threshold computation: **~15-25% reduction** (18.36 → ~14-16 ms) due to faster lookups
- **Overall expected timing**: 82.56 ms → **~65-75 ms** (20-27% improvement)

